					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1663957#post-2483382</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1663957/not-a-contest-entry-but-a-crackfic-about-gods-anyways#post-2483382</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 01 Apr 2016 15:54:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>SunnyClockwork</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1621343</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Since this tale went better than I expected I guess I'll put a reference list here :P</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;List&nbsp;of&nbsp;things&nbsp;that&nbsp;appeared</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;List&nbsp;of&nbsp;things&nbsp;that&nbsp;appeared</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The Great Abyss - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/sarkicism-hub">Sarkicism Hub</a> (Mythology tab)<br /> DEER - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2845">SCP-2845</a> - THE DEER<br /> Daleport - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1936">SCP-1936</a> - Daleport<br /> <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/system:page-tags/tag/pangloss#pages">Pangloss</a><br /> Pattern Screamers - Well, they appeared in a number of articles and are not clear in nature<br /> MEKHANE - <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/system:page-tags/tag/broken-god#pages">The Broken God</a><br /> Yaldabaoth - <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/system:page-tags/tag/sarkic#pages">The Sarkic God</a><br /> Archons - Servants of Yaldabaoth<br /> Scarlet King - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2317">SCP-2317</a> - A Door to Another World<br /> Ptah and his wife - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2343">SCP-2343</a> - How I Got To Memphis<br /> The Hanged King - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-701">SCP-701</a> - The Hanged King's Tragedy<br /> He-Who-Made-Light and his brother - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-435">SCP-435</a> - “He-Who-Made-Dark”<br /> Me, aka the toaster - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/hello-i-am-an-eldritch-horror">Hello, I Am an Eldritch Horror</a><br /> Starfish god/Fifth God - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/case-colourless-green">CASE COLOURLESS GREEN</a><br /> He-Who-Walks-Beneath-Dreams - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1936">SCP-1936</a> - Daleport</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Aslo credit to Perelka_L for the idea of gods' party came up in discussions with her. Great thanks Decibelle, TwistedGears and Metaphysician for helping with the tale.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
